(31, 13, 'Stanley', 'It''s not gonna end like this.', 1, '2015-01-21 18:39:00', '2015-01-21 18:39:00'),
(32, 13, 'Gabriel', 'Oh, come on, Stan. Not everything ends the way you think it should. Besides, audiences love happy endings.', 1, '2015-01-21 18:39:00', '2015-01-21 18:39:00'),
(33, 15, 'Mile', 'Doesn''t Bill Gates have something like that?', 1, '2015-01-21 18:39:00', '2015-01-21 18:39:00'),
(34, 15, 'Gary', 'Bill Who?', 1, '2015-01-21 18:39:00', '2015-01-21 18:39:00');
